sentences: Katarina Grujić Gobeljić (Serbian Cyrillic: Катарина Грујић Гобељић; born 20 May 1992) is a Serbian pop-folk singer who rose to prominence as a contestant on the televised singing competition Zvezde Granda in 2012, finishing in eighth place.

Katarina Grujić Gobeljić (Serbian Cyrillic: Катарина Грујић Гобељић; born 20 May 1992) is a Serbian pop-folk singer who rose to prominence as a contestant on the televised singing competition Zvezde Granda in 2012, finishing in eighth place.
In August 2021, Grujić married Serbian footballer Marko Gobeljić.
She gave birth to their daughter in December the same year.
